OpenXT OpenEmbedded metadata
============================

This repository hosts the OpenXT OpenEmbedded/Yocto **meta-layers**.

Layers
------

See **LAYERS.md** for layout, dependencies, and `bblayers.conf` examples.

| Directory | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `meta-openxt-base` | Headless dom0, toolstack, security, installer, stubdomain |
| `meta-openxt-domains` | NDVM, USBVM, SyncVM service domain images |
| `meta-openxt-ui` | UIVM and optional dom0 UI/display integration |

Plan and inventory
------------------

- `BUILD_PLAN.md` — layer-split design and phases
- `docs/INVENTORY.md` — Phase 0 static inventory (pre-split snapshot notes)

External documentation
----------------------

- Website: http://openxt.org
- Build wiki: https://github.com/OpenXT/openxt/wiki/

